Class Summary
Account A generic account
AccountLimitLog Logs every change of either lower or upper credit limit on an account
AccountLock AccountLocks just contains the account relationship and are used to lock accounts, independent of the account themselves, as locking accounts could have several other impacts, like not allowing inserting transfers from/to that account
AccountQuery  
AccountRates  
AccountStatus Holds the current status for a given account

BaseTransferAmountReservation Base class for reservations related to a transfer
ClosedAccountBalance Contains the pre-calculated balance and amount reservation for an account at a given date.
Currency An account type currency
DRateParameters The parameters needed for a currency when D-rate is enabled.
InitializableRateParameters Parent class for ARateParameters and DRateParameters classes.
InstallmentAmountReservation A returned amount reservation by an installment of a scheduled payment which reserved the whole amount
IRateParameters Parameters for configuration of the I-rate.
MemberAccount An account owned by a member
MemberAccountType Type for member accounts
MemberGroupAccountSettings This is an associative class between MemberGroup and MemberAccountType.
PendingAuthorizationAmountReservation An amount reservation by a payment pending authorization
RateParameters parent class for all RateParameters.
ScheduledPaymentAmountReservation An amount reservation by a scheduled payment which reserves the whole amount
SystemAccount A system account.
SystemAccountOwner This class represents the owner for system accounts
SystemAccountType Type for system accounts
TransferAuthorizationAmountReservation A returned amount reservation by a transfer authorization
